innowing pounded grain The artistry of these baskets is being steadily enhanced color improved designs as they are increasingly produced for commercial useOther notable artistic communities include Pottery Weavers both located in the southeastern part of BotswanaThe oldest paintings from both Botswana South Africa depict hunting animal human figures were made the Khoisan Kung SanBushmen over twenty thousand years ago the Kalahari desertIn addition to these more traditional arts are a number of extremely talented artists use modern means to express There are a few galleries Botswana that display paintings and sculptures Some pieces are inspired the beautiful Botswana landscapes and others by the people themselvesCuisineImageBoerewors rawjpgthumbright200pxBoereworsThe cuisine of Botswana is unique also shares characteristics with other cuisine of Africa Examples of Botswana food are Pap Boerewors Samp Vetkoek and worms A food unique to Botswana includes Seswaa heavily salted mashedup meatHolidaysImageMiss Botswana 08 Itseng KgomotsojpgthumbuprightKgomotso Miss Botswana 2008 Miss World 2008See alsoof Nationsin Botswanaof Botswanastamps and postal history of Bechuanaland Protectoratein BotswanablockNotes and referencesFurther reading Alexander McCall Smith The No1 Ladies Detective Agency series Michael Stanley A Carrion Death part of the Detective Kubu seriesExternal links httpwwwbotswanaportalcomlist listaceBotswanaafBotswanaalsBotsuanaamangBotswanaaranBotswanaroarupBotswanafrpBotsouanaastBotsuanaazBotsvanabmBotswanabnzhminnanBotswanabebexoldbclBotswanabobsBocvanabrBotswanabgcaBotswanacvcebBotswanacsBotswanacyBotswanadaBotswanapdcBotswanadeBotsuanadvDine BikyahetBotswanaelesBotsuanaeoBocvanoextBotsuanaeuBotswanaeeBotswanafahifBotswanafoBotsvanafrBotswanafyBotswanaffBotswanaBhotsuinVotswaangagBotsvanagdBotsuanade Botsuana Republic of 
